        <sect1>
            <title>Gebetan</title>

            <para>
                Gebetan is the philosophy followed by the cult of
                Tharos. It teaches personal perfection above all else,
                both in body and mind. A person must continuously push
                themselves to their limit, for that is seen as the only
                way to push beyond those limits and improve.
            </para>

            <para>
                The Art of Gebetan is also a legendary style of combat,
                through which a practitioner can achieve physical feats
                beyond the capability of normal men.
            </para>
        </sect1>
